# MasternodeSetup

### Required:

1. Coins for Collateral <br>

2. Download Local Wallet for your operating system: : https://github.com/Roicoinorg/Roicoinorg/releases/tag/1000


3. You will need also VPS with Ubuntu 16.04 or 18.04 or 20.04

**VPS WALLET:**

To install mnsc Masternode use the following command:

`bash <( curl -sL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Roicoinorg/Masternodesetup/master/masternode-install.sh)

- Enjoy

check your masternode status using `roicoin-cli getmasternodestatus` after run it from local wallet


